title: Letter by Joseph Raynes, in Baltimore, to his Family, 1 September 1834
summary: Letter written by Joseph Raynes from Baltimore, Maryland, to his family in Bonsall, Derbyshire, England, 1 September 1834. Describes life in Baltimore and the failure of the Bank of Maryland.

title: Letter by Joseph Raynes, in Liverpool, to his Family, 10 May 1831
summary: Letter written by Joseph Raynes from Liverpool to his family in Bonsall, Derbyshire, England 10 May 1831. Describes the brig "Russian," on which he has reserved a space to travel to Baltimore, Maryland.
